@startuml
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #f8fafc
  BorderColor #475569
}

title 分层架构与职责分离示意图

rectangle "表示层\nVue 页面 / 路由 / Pinia" as Presentation
rectangle "接口层\nController" as Controller
rectangle "业务层\nService" as Service
rectangle "持久层\nRepository" as Repository
rectangle "领域对象\nEntity / DTO" as Domain
rectangle "数据库\nMigration + Tables" as Database

Presentation --> Controller : HTTP / JSON
Controller --> Service : 当前用户 + 业务请求
Service --> Repository : 查询 / 保存
Repository --> Domain : 映射实体
Repository --> Database : 持久化
Service --> Domain : 组装结果
Controller --> Presentation : ApiResponse

note right of Service
典型模式：
- 控制器只取当前用户并转发
- 业务规则集中在 Service
- 统一响应与异常由 common 层收口
end note

@enduml
